thread.title: BRIEF-Nippon Prologis REIT says new unit prices

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Nippon Prologis REIT says new unit prices
text:
March 5 (Reuters) - Nippon Prologis REIT Inc
* Says it will issue new units via public offering, with the issue price of 224,812 yen per unit (or 27.62 billion yen in total) and paid-in price of 217,448 yen per unit (or 26.72 billion yen in total)
* Says it will issue new units via private placement, with the paid-in price of 217,448 yen per unit (or up to 1.34 billion yen in total)
Source text in Japanese: goo.gl/gGjKaE
